    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, pulling strongly to the 8,000 RPM redline. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including a recent VANOS service and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains taut with M-spec suspension and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution translates to exceptional corner-exit traction. This is a mechanically sound, turn-key example for the enthusiast who values tactile feedback and analog performance.",
